trans-unit.source: Defines an encoder that is used to encode [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wdp](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wdp-md.md)] images.
trans-unit.target: Definerer en koder som brukes til å kryptere [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wdp](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wdp-md.md)] bilder.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wdp](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] is a new codec that provides better image fidelity than [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_jpegorg](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] with smaller file sizes and more features.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wdp](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]en ny kodek som gir bedre bildegjengivelse enn [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_jpegorg](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] med mindre filstørrelser og flere funksjoner.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wdp](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] images achieve lossy and lossless compression by using a single algorithm.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wdp](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]bilder for komprimering med og uten tap komprimering ved hjelp av en enkelt algoritmen.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wdp](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] images support existing metadata standards.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wdp](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]bilder støtter eksisterende metadata standarder.

trans-unit.source: For additional information about this format, see [Windows Media Photo Specification](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/wmphoto.mspx).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om dette formatet i [Windows Media Photo spesifikasjonen](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/wmphoto.mspx).

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wdp](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] files do not support preview, global thumbnails, frame level thumbnails, or multiple frames.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wdp](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]filer støtter ikke forhåndsvisning, globale miniatyrbilder, ramme nivå miniatyrbilder eller flere bilder.

trans-unit.source: Encoding does not work in partial trust.
trans-unit.target: Koding fungerer ikke med delvis klarering.

trans-unit.source: See [WPF Partial Trust Security](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) for information on partial trust.
trans-unit.target: Se [WPF delvis klarering sikkerhet](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) for informasjon om delvis klarering.

trans-unit.source: ## XAML Text Usage
trans-unit.target: ## XAML teksten Bruk

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the level of alpha frequency data to discard during a compressed domain transcode.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir alfa frekvens dataene forkaste under en komprimert domene omkode.

trans-unit.source: This property has an effect only if <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.CompressedDomainTranscode%2A> is set to `true` and the image contains either a planar or interleaved alpha channel; otherwise, it is ignored.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen har en effekt hvis <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.CompressedDomainTranscode%2A>er satt til `true` og bildet inneholder enten en plan eller innfelt alfa kanal; ellers ignoreres.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.CompressedDomainTranscode%2A>

trans-unit.source: ## XAML Text Usage
trans-unit.target: ## XAML teksten Bruk

trans-unit.source: The level of alpha data to discard when encoding the image.
trans-unit.target: Datanivået alfa forkaste når koding bildet.

trans-unit.source: The value range is 0 (no data discarded) to 4 (alpha channel completely discarded).
trans-unit.target: Verdiområdet er 0 (ingen data forkastet) til 4 (alfa kanal fullstendig forkastet).

trans-unit.source: The default is 1.
trans-unit.target: Standard er 1.

trans-unit.source: Value
trans-unit.target: Verdi

trans-unit.source: Description
trans-unit.target: Beskrivelse

trans-unit.source: No image frequency data is discarded.
trans-unit.target: Ingen data frekvens forkastes.

trans-unit.source: FlexBits are discarded.
trans-unit.target: FlexBits forkastes.

trans-unit.source: The image quality of the image is reduced without changing the effective resolution of the image.
trans-unit.target: Bildekvaliteten på bildet reduseres uten å endre den effektive oppløsningen for bildet.

trans-unit.source: HighPass frequency data band is discarded.
trans-unit.target: HighPass frekvens dataene utenforliggende forkastes.

trans-unit.source: The image's effective resolution is reduced by a factor of 4 in both dimensions.
trans-unit.target: Bildets effektiv oppløsning reduseres med en skalaverdi på 4 i begge dimensjonene.

trans-unit.source: HighPass and LowPass frequency data bands are discarded.
trans-unit.target: HighPass og LowPass frekvens dataene verdiområder forkastes.

trans-unit.source: The image's effective resolution is reduced by a factor of 16 in both dimensions.
trans-unit.target: Bildets effektiv oppløsning reduseres med en skalaverdi på 16 i begge dimensjonene.

trans-unit.source: The alpha channel is completely discarded.
trans-unit.target: Alfa kanalen forkastes fullstendig.

trans-unit.source: The pixel format is changed to reflect the removal of the alpha channel.
trans-unit.target: Pikselformatet er endret for å gjenspeile fjerning av alfa kanalen.

trans-unit.source: The value given is not between 0 and 4.
trans-unit.target: Verdien som er angitt, er ikke mellom 0 og 4.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the compression quality for a planar alpha channel.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir komprimeringskvaliteten for en plan alfa kanal.

trans-unit.source: This property has an effect only if <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.InterleavedAlpha%2A> is `false`.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen har en effekt hvis <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.InterleavedAlpha%2A>er `false`.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.InterleavedAlpha%2A>

trans-unit.source: ## XAML Text Usage
trans-unit.target: ## XAML teksten Bruk

trans-unit.source: The compression quality for a planar alpha channel image.
trans-unit.target: Komprimeringskvaliteten for en plan alfa kanal bildet.

trans-unit.source: A value of 1 is considered lossless, and increasing values result in higher compression ratios and lower image quality.
trans-unit.target: Verdien 1 anses datatap og økende føre til høyere komprimeringsforhold og lavere bildekvalitet.

trans-unit.source: The value range is 1 to 255.
trans-unit.target: Verdien er 1 til 255.

trans-unit.source: The default is 1.
trans-unit.target: Standard er 1.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether compressed domain operations can be used.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om komprimert domene operasjoner kan brukes.

trans-unit.source: Compressed domain operations are transformation operations that are done without decoding the image data.
trans-unit.target: Komprimert domene operasjoner er transformasjonen operasjoner som er brukt uten dekoding image-data.

trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om koding i frekvens rekkefølge.

trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>kode bildet i frekvens rekkefølge. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> kode bildet av den avstandsdata retningen.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the number of horizontal divisions to use during compression encoding.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir antall vannrette fordelinger skal brukes under komprimering koding.

trans-unit.source: A single division creates two horizontal regions.
trans-unit.target: En enkelt divisjon oppretter to vannrette områder.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.CompressedDomainTranscode%2A> is `true`, HorizontalTileSlices must be set to 0.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.CompressedDomainTranscode%2A>er `true`, HorizontalTileSlices må settes til 0.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.CompressedDomainTranscode%2A>

trans-unit.source: A tile created by the division can never be smaller than 16 pixels.
trans-unit.target: En flis opprettet av divisjonen kan aldri være mindre enn 16 piksler.

trans-unit.source: The value is adjusted to maintain the minimum tile size.
trans-unit.target: Verdien er endret for å beholde minste flisstørrelsen.

trans-unit.source: When used in combination with <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.VerticalTileSlices%2A>, a grid of tiles is formed.
trans-unit.target: Når det brukes sammen med <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.VerticalTileSlices%2A>, et rutenett med fliser er utformet.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.VerticalTileSlices%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if both properties are set to 1, the image is divided into 4 tiles.
trans-unit.target: Hvis begge egenskapene er satt til 1, er for eksempel bildet inndelt i 4 fliser.

trans-unit.source: ## XAML Text Usage
trans-unit.target: ## XAML teksten Bruk

trans-unit.source: The number of horizontal divisions to use during compression encoding.
trans-unit.target: Antall vannrette fordelinger skal brukes under komprimering koding.

trans-unit.source: The value range is 0 to 4095.
trans-unit.target: Verdien er 0 til 4095.

trans-unit.source: The default is 0.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er 0.

trans-unit.target: Bildekvaliteten på bildet reduseres uten å endre den effektive oppløsningen for bildet.

trans-unit.source: HighPass frequency data band is discarded.

trans-unit.source: The image's effective resolution is reduced by a factor of 4 in both dimensions.

trans-unit.source: The overlap processing level.
trans-unit.target: Overlapper behandling nivået.

trans-unit.source: The default is 1.
trans-unit.target: Standard er 1.

trans-unit.source: Value
trans-unit.target: Verdi

trans-unit.source: Description
trans-unit.target: Beskrivelse

trans-unit.source: No overlap processing is enabled.
trans-unit.target: Ingen overlapper-behandling er aktivert.

trans-unit.source: One level of overlap processing is enabled.
trans-unit.target: Ett nivå med overlapper behandling er aktivert.

trans-unit.source: Encoded values of 4x4 blocks are modified based on the values of neighboring blocks.
trans-unit.target: Kodet verdier for 4 x 4 er endret basert på verdier i nærliggende blokker.

trans-unit.target: I tillegg til det første nivået i behandling endres kodet verdier for 16 x 16 makroer basert på verdier i nærliggende makroer blokker.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates codec options are to be used.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir kodeken alternativer som skal brukes.

trans-unit.source: When UseCodecOptions is `true`, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.QualityLevel%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.OverlapLevel%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.SubsamplingLevel%2A> are used in place of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.ImageQualityLevel%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Når UseCodecOptions er `true`, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.QualityLevel%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.OverlapLevel%2A>, og <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.SubsamplingLevel%2A>brukes i stedet <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.ImageQualityLevel%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.ImageQualityLevel%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.SubsamplingLevel%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.OverlapLevel%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.QualityLevel%2A>

trans-unit.source: When UseCodecOptions is `false`, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.QualityLevel%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.OverlapLevel%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.SubsamplingLevel%2A> are set based on <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.ImageQualityLevel%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Når UseCodecOptions er `false`, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.QualityLevel%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.OverlapLevel%2A>, og <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.SubsamplingLevel%2A>er angitt basert på <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.ImageQualityLevel%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.ImageQualityLevel%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.SubsamplingLevel%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.OverlapLevel%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.QualityLevel%2A>

trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis kodeken alternativene som skal brukes; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the number of vertical divisions to use during compression encoding.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir antallet loddrette fordelinger skal brukes under komprimering koding.

trans-unit.source: A single division creates two vertical regions.
trans-unit.target: En enkelt divisjon oppretter to loddrette områder.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.CompressedDomainTranscode%2A> is `true`, VerticalTileSlices must be set to 0.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.CompressedDomainTranscode%2A>er `true`, VerticalTileSlices må settes til 0.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.CompressedDomainTranscode%2A>

trans-unit.source: A tile created by the division can never be smaller than 16 pixels.
trans-unit.target: En flis opprettet av divisjonen kan aldri være mindre enn 16 piksler.

trans-unit.source: The value is adjusted to maintain the minimum tile size.
trans-unit.target: Verdien er endret for å beholde minste flisstørrelsen.

trans-unit.source: When used in combination with <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.HorizontalTileSlices%2A>, a grid of tiles is formed.
trans-unit.target: Når det brukes sammen med <xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.HorizontalTileSlices%2A>, et rutenett med fliser er utformet.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Imaging.WmpBitmapEncoder.HorizontalTileSlices%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if both properties are set to 1, the image is divided into 4 tiles.
trans-unit.target: Hvis begge egenskapene er satt til 1, er for eksempel bildet inndelt i 4 fliser.

trans-unit.source: The number of vertical divisions to use during compression encoding.
trans-unit.target: Antall loddrette fordelinger skal brukes under komprimering koding.

trans-unit.source: The value range is 0 to 4095.
trans-unit.target: Verdien er 0 til 4095.

trans-unit.source: The default is 0.
